column16: Jay Bruce pops out to second baseman Willie Bloomquist.
Devin Mesoraco singles on a line drive to center fielder Gerardo Parra.   Derrick Robinson scores.
Jack Hannahan flies out to left fielder Jason Kubel.
Derrick Robinson singles on a line drive to center fielder Gerardo Parra, deflected by pitcher Joe Paterson.
Xavier Paul grounds out, second baseman Willie Bloomquist to first baseman Paul Goldschmidt.
Ryan Hanigan grounds into a double play, shortstop Didi Gregorius to second baseman Willie Bloomquist to first baseman Paul Goldschmidt.   Todd Frazier to 3rd.    Zack Cozart out at 2nd.
Zack Cozart hit by pitch.    Todd Frazier to 2nd.
